Achievements.Title: Rest in peace, Siras
Achievements.Description: Finish 'The Road to Oebalus' less than or equal to 1:10s.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Freedom
Achievements.Description: Save 6 hostages in 'The Pirate King Pactolus'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: How about using eye drops?
Achievements.Description: Finish 'The Isles of Kronos' less than or equal to 1:10s.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Bloodthirsty
Achievements.Description: Defeat 30 enemies in 'On the Trail of Gabrielle'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: When cows fly
Achievements.Description: Destroy the camp and the fort in 'Valarian's Castle', the catapult user will throw a cow on you.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Now I like catapults
Achievements.Description: Use the catapult and destroy the fort in 'Valarian's Secret'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: The Minotaur
Achievements.Description: Don't use any item in 'The Labyrinth'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Power of Gods
Achievements.Description: In 'The Renegade Amazon Village' use Promethean Blade, Hand of Zeus and Frost Biter in any sequence.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Red River
Achievements.Description: Defeat 35 enemies in 'Rivers of Blood', without Frost Biter usage.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: The Amazon Queen
Achievements.Description: Don't use any item in 'Lost Temple of the Titans'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: The Dragon
Achievements.Description: Finish 'Dyzan's Lair' less than or equal to 1min.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Tartarus
Achievements.Description: Don't use any item in 'Road to Hades'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Skull Collector
Achievements.Description: Defeat 65 enemies in 'Traps of Charon' without using Resurrection Jewel.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Underworld
Achievements.Description: Finish 'Hades' Castle' less than or equal to 1:40s.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Red Snow
Achievements.Description: Defeat 20 enemies in 'The Village of T'ir Na', without Frost Biter usage.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: The Seer
Achievements.Description: Save Fei with 100% of his health bar.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Yat, The Druid Sorcerer
Achievements.Description: Don't use any item in 'The Lyre of Orpheus'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Gorgons
Achievements.Description: Don't use Resurrection Jewel or Golden Shield in 'The Three Sisters'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Kalabrax
Achievements.Description: Don't use any item in 'The Temple of the Pinnacles'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Chrysus
Achievements.Description: Activate a Golden Shield in 'The Pirate King Pactolus' and 'The Challenge'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Hephaestus
Achievements.Description: Have 2x Promethean Blade in 'Rescue the Seer, Fei'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Despoina
Achievements.Description: Activate a Frost Biter in 'The Renegade Amazon Village' and 'Rivers of Blood'.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos

Achievements.Title: Rare Scrolls
Achievements.Description: Obtain all scrolls in one sitting, collecting both per stage.

Achievements.Title: Training Mode
Achievements.Description: Collect at least 10 potions and 3 golden shields in 'Training Arena'.

Achievements.Description: Find the developers' secret room in 'The Labyrinth', then hit the computer.
Achievements.Author: raniejogos
